                     <interp inst="t18321129-11-person214" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I received the handkerchief from the prosecutor - the prisoners denied the charge.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18321129-11-person215">
                  Francis 
                  Wiltshire
               <interp inst="t18321129-11-person215" type="surname" value="Wiltshire"></interp>
